{"tid":1609358,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民灑溪錢","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:32:26.000Z","uid":77666,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df57f1a6a2d915ab49c74219fe1feb88e9a90752","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"返左屋企既你, 由於今日係國殤, 只係係發夢地方灑溪錢係唔夠, 我地需要全港十八區齊齊灑, 畫面先夠震撼, 聽日起身見到全部地方都係白色呢個畫面先夠震撼。 由於溪錢呢個時間已經買唔到, 個人認為溪錢形式不限, 可以係紙巾、A4紙之類&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n小弟提供以下方案, 可以用一般家庭裝既一大卷紙巾, 然後整開每一舊, 基本上一圈紙巾, 已經可以提供極大量既「溪錢」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRAwhJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRAwhJp.png&h=7545951a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tfv0Vvb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfv0Vvb.png&h=fef2795d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTW若果放的話 千其唔好係自己單位放, 盡可能係LIFT口大堂 / 防煙門後門&hellip;同埋要留意風向同CCTV位置。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&ndash; 咁開心既日子 緊係要齊齊賀佢老母 當然你亦可以當哀度中槍義士<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&ndash; 都係唔好啦 搞到清潔姐姐就唔好 仲可能會塞左啲渠添 又浪費啲紙巾"},{"pid":"6d4400eb6a70e3d03877c1f4fbfdf476c57df19f","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"100"},{"pid":"26a1e28b4aedf15414089cc4e15555a68e1a67f0","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"99"},{"pid":"f66f77b7187c09cd8398bb421d9b532853814176","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"98"},{"pid":"f4a1bdc815b77d6fba346d717e9fd7fefc4794d7","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"97"},{"pid":"d8ff7b2f4f3fd5e96343254d54030c91679e2690","tid":1609358,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:24:3